Volvere PLC (VLE)



Volvere PLC

Posting of Annual Report and Notice of AGM

RNS Number : 9524Z Volvere PLC 01 June 2016  

 
1 June 2016
 
Volvere plc 
("Volvere" or the "Company")
 
Posting of Annual Report and Financial Statements and Notice of AGM
Volvere announces that is has today posted to shareholders, notice of its annual general meeting, to be held at 3.00 p.m. at Marriott Harrison LLP, 11 Staple Inn, London WC1V 7QH on 28 June 2016 (the "AGM"), together with hard copies (for those shareholders who have not elected to receive electronic communication from the Company) of its Annual Report and Financial Statements (the "Annual Report") for the financial year ended 31 December 2015.  
The Annual Report and the notice of the AGM will shortly be made available on the Company's website, www.volvere.co.uk 
For further information contact:
 




Volvere plc
Jonathan Lander, CEO
Nick Lander, COO
 


 Tel: +44 20 7634 9707




N+1 Singer
Aubrey Powell
Liz Yong


Tel: + 44 20 7496 3000




 
 
 

This information is provided by RNSThe company news service from the London Stock Exchange   END  ACSSSLFMFFMSESM











