29 May 2015




 
 
 
Volvere plc
 
("Volvere" or the "Group")
 
Final results for the year ended 31 December 2014
 
Volvere plc (AIM: VLE), the growth and turnaround investment company, announces its final results for the year ended 31 December 2014.
 
